  <brief_title>Efficiency of Ventilation During Conscious Sedation in the Pediatric Intensive Care Unit</brief_title>
  <official_title>Efficiency of Ventilation During Conscious Sedation of Pediatric Patients Undergoing Minor Procedures in the Pediatric Intensive Care Unit</official_title>
